                    <span>I was very moved by Lessons of the Game and what Derek Sparks had to say. As a first time author, I think he is a very good writer. It encouraging to see athletes prosper off the field. I look forward to reading his next book. It was very brave of him to step up to the plate and deliver. I could not put this book down when I started to read it. As a parent I was concerned by the things that go on under the table. Lessons of the Game will be a required reading in my house hold. Thank you Derek for your sincere care for our youth. <P>Guy Thomas</span>
                  
